{
  "id": "api-hang-001",
  "version": 1,
  "title": "固まった API の夜",
  "difficulty": "intermediate",
  "difficultyScore": 210,
  "timeLimitMinutes": 10,
  "service": {
    "name": "やまびこ API",
    "healthUrl": "http://localhost:8080/health"
  },
  "briefing": [
    "プロセスが「死んでいる」のと「固まっている」のは別の障害。",
    "curl は返ってこない。でもプロセスは生きている。その状態を切り分ける。",
    "ps の STAT 列が読めると強い。"
  ],
  "startup": [
    {
      "id": "api",
      "command": "PORT=8080 node /workspace/services/yamabiko-api/server.mjs",
      "waitForPort": 8080
    },
    {
      "id": "fake-db",
      "command": "node /workspace/services/fake-db/server.mjs",
      "waitForPort": 15432
    }
  ],
  "topology": {
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "user",
        "label": "ユーザー",
        "kind": "external"
      },
      {
        "id": "api",
        "label": "やまびこ API",
        "kind": "service",
        "processId": "api"
      },
      {
        "id": "fake-db",
        "label": "疑似データベース",
        "kind": "datastore",
        "processId": "fake-db"
      }
    ],
    "edges": [
      {
        "from": "user",
        "to": "api"
      },
      {
        "from": "api",
        "to": "fake-db"
      }
    ]
  },
  "triggers": [
    {
      "id": "hang",
      "atMs": 60000,
      "type": "process_hang",
      "params": {
        "processId": "api"
      }
    }
  ],
  "alerts": [
    {
      "id": "latency",
      "atMs": 80000,
      "severity": "critical",
      "message": "API latency p95 is above 5s",
      "source": "monitor"
    },
    {
      "id": "health-fail",
      "atMs": 95000,
      "severity": "critical",
      "message": "やまびこ API health check failed",
      "source": "monitor"
    }
  ],
  "successConditions": [
    {
      "type": "http_status",
      "url": "http://localhost:8080/health",
      "status": 200
    },
    {
      "type": "process_running",
      "processId": "api"
    }
  ],
  "runbooks": [
    {
      "id": "runbook.hang",
      "title": "ハングの切り分け",
      "body": "1. curl --max-time 3 localhost:8080/health で応答を見る\n   (返ってこない=タイムアウトも重要な情報)\n2. yamactl status api。プロセスが生きているのに応答しないなら「ハング」\n3. ps -o pid,stat,cmd で状態を確認する。STAT が T なら停止シグナルで固まっている\n4. 直近の app.log に前兆(GC pause など)がないか見る\n5. yamactl restart api で強制再起動し、health で復旧確認する"
    }
  ],
  "chatMessages": [
    {
      "id": "boss-hang",
      "atMs": 115000,
      "from": "上司",
      "body": "落ちてはいないんでしょ？なら大丈夫じゃない。おやすみ。"
    }
  ],
  "navigationSteps": [
    {
      "id": "nav-latency",
      "atMs": 0,
      "hint": "Latency p95 が急上昇していないか見る",
      "panel": "metrics"
    },
    {
      "id": "nav-curl",
      "atMs": 65000,
      "hint": "タイムアウト付きで応答を確認する",
      "panel": "terminal",
      "suggestedCommand": "curl --max-time 3 localhost:8080/health"
    }
  ]
}
